  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nMailservers from `eth.prod`  fail to connect. On iOS when tapping on `An error occured while fetching history` the `Mailserver request error` pop-up appears.\r\nSame with RC.\r\n\r\nSwitching to eth.staging make things working fine\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nCan connect to mailservers and fetch history\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nCan not connect to mailserver and no history fetched\r\n\r\n<img width=\"286\" alt=\"Screenshot 2020-01-22 at 11 44 28\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/72883203-919b5700-3d0c-11ea-9b79-1c12980e994b.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n- Install Status develop build \r\n- Open Status and create new account\r\n- Join public chat\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: develop 2020012208 (nightly 22nd of January)\r\n- Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\n```\r\n01-22 11:48:22.932   970   970 D ScrollView:  onsize change changed \r\n01-22 11:48:22.932   970   970 D ScrollView:  onsize change changed \r\n01-22 11:48:22.934   970   970 D ViewRootImpl@d8a9faf[MainActivity]: MSG_WINDOW_FOCUS_CHANGED 1 1\r\n01-22 11:48:22.951   970   970 D ViewRootImpl@d8a9faf[MainActivity]: MSG_RESIZED: frame=Rect(27, 744 - 1053, 1403) ci=Rect(0, 0 - 0, 0) vi=Rect(0, 0 - 0, 0) or=1\r\n01-22 11:48:22.974   970   970 D ViewRootImpl@f9e1fbf[MainActivity]: MSG_WINDOW_FOCUS_CHANGED 0 1\r\n01-22 11:48:22.974   970   970 D InputMethodManager: prepareNavigationBarInfo() DecorView@b6a723a[MainActivity]\r\n01-22 11:48:22.974   970   970 D InputMethodManager: getNavigationBarColor() -855310\r\n01-22 11:48:24.012   970  1021 E GoLog   : ERROR[01-22|09:48:24.011] failed to dowload transfers using concurrent downloader error=nil\r\n01-22 11:48:24.012   970  1576 E GoLog   : ERROR[01-22|09:48:24.012] failed to dowload transfers using concurrent downloader error=nil\r\n01-22