    "body": "The problem is because of this change: https://github.com/status-im/status-go/pull/1805/files#diff-f422bb8b8162ca6a8f7fbff615267548R382. Mailserver (or the app) requiers `Topics` field while the other side does not understand it and deserialization breaks producing garbage as you see in the alert.\r\n\r\nWe need to align status-go used on the mailservers and in the app. ",
